          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张紫艳脱衣帽。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张紫艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家就是歌姬张紫艳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来就是小娘子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张紫艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喏奴家呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（索南枝） 怎忍见英雄汉餐宝刀，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此乔妆悄然告尔曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 你把这支令箭呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（索南枝） 急忙奔出潼关，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急去偷生好！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼 （索南枝） 感深恩天样高，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘重生，粉身报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张紫艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺秦琼就此去也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（索南枝） 鳌鱼脱金钩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几次行止还止。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张紫艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊小娘子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张紫艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去了怎么又转来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小娘子我去便去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（索南枝） 岂可贻累姣娥，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "反惹人嘲笑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺秦琼为朋友而死，理所当然，岂可累及小娘子？于心何忍也！罢，不如仍旧\n回营，凭大王处置便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张紫艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军此身架海擎天，关系非小。奴家一身与草木同腐，何必虑及啊！必须当面\n决断，你才放心！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（索南枝） 把微躯委短蒿，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女英雄万年表！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张紫艳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军你看那边官兵来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张紫艳自刎，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，你看小娘子自刎了！哎呀小娘子吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扑灯蛾） 看英风天与齐，看英风天与齐，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愧我须眉苟活也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 小娘子吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扑灯蛾） 鞠躬拜倒，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日里权堆荒草。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦琼拭目。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼 （扑灯蛾） 痛孤魂，香醪一滴有谁浇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，小娘子已死，哭也无益。不免骑了黄骠马，连夜奔出潼关便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我双手撇开生死路——"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一身跳出是非门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦琼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀小娘子吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦琼悲下。）"
        }
      ],
