    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "上官仪",
        "杨林",
        "贺芳"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四兵卒引杨林同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "日月依龙德，风云挟豹韬。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨林上高座。贺芳急上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺芳",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忙将破胆惊天事，报与金枝玉叶人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王在上，贺芳打躬交令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦琼拿到了么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贺芳奉大王钧旨去拿秦琼。说他昨夜黄昏，有一尊官手持令箭，说奉大王将令，\n差往潼关公干，连夜走了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那军官一定是奸细，查出一同处斩！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺芳允。上官仪急上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "上官仪",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别号人中杰，威分阃外司。"
        },
        {
          "character": "上官仪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上官仪打躬交令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上官仪回来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "上官仪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你郊外巡缉，怎么样了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "上官仪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉命郊外巡哨，见一被杀妇人，身穿男子衣帽。仔细检验，原来是歌姬张紫艳。\n特来报知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！一定是这贱人窃听消息，盗孤令箭，报知秦琼。可恼吓可恼！\n上官仪听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上官仪允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取我令箭一支，赶上秦琼。说孤毫不见怪，唤他转来，还要重用。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上官仪允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "上官仪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "上官仪",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一心忙似箭，加鞭走如飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上官仪下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贺芳启上大王：上官仪此去，秦琼决不转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就看你带五百铁骑擒回便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺芳",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺芳下。杨林下高座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贺芳不是秦琼对手，待孤亲自走遭。秦琼秦琼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这回好似泰山来压卵，须知螳臂怎当车！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨林、四兵卒同下。）"
        }
      ],
